flowRoot.flowPara: For important buttons, such as OK and Save. One such button should exist in any view and it should be denoted in QML as primary: true. The word primary will be used in other controls too
Other buttons should have this look.
Pressed button. While being pushed, the button will glow where the user's thumb is. This can be achieved by putting an image at the right coordinates.
Pressed important button. Keep in mind that the glow will be usually covered by one's thumb
